I just served this for Christmas Eve lunch to rave reviews. I'm printing the recipe for my Mom, which is why I stopped to write a review. Very easy, but is elegant enough to impress. I made it yesterday, and put it all together today. Works great! I was surprised at how light it was despite the amount of heavy and sour cream.

